PROFILE_DESCRIPTION: Shows the profile of a user
GIF_ENABLED: {{author}} Your profile has GIF feature enabled. To load your GIF profile use the `{{prefix}}pc` command and click on the `Reload GIF profile` button in the dropdown menu
PROFILE_EXTRA_INFO: Shows the players profile. Using this command without a prompt will show your profile, adding another player's username or user id will show their profile. You can customize your profile by using the "{{prefix}}profileconfig" command
